      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "Database health for a single Data Platform account, using auto-published CloudWatch metrics. Pick an **Account** at the top. This dashboard provides a first-look operational view across RDS/Aurora and DynamoDB. It highlights saturation, latency, storage pressure, connection pressure and throttling. Empty panels usually mean that the service is not present in the selected account." }
